aim_sniper_race
Created By Naticus 3/28/2010
http://www.jgcclan.net/

Intro:
=======
This is a sniper racing map.  Shoot the targets at each station to open the door to the next area to score one kill each.
Finishing the course first will score you 3 kills plus eliminate the other side! Don't miss with the AWP 
or it will mean a time consuming reload.   

Footnote:
=========
Thanks to Swampy Turtle for a great idea and to the JGC Clan for their support.
